---
layout: page.njk
title: home
ogImage: https://v1.screenshot.11ty.dev/https%3A%2F%2Fwilliamwhitaker.dev/opengraph/
ogDesc: Hi I'm William and this is my website
pagination:
  data: collections.posts
  size: 5
  alias: posts
templateEngineOverride: njk, md
---
<article class="flow">
  <h2>about me</h2>
{% snippet %}

I'm William. Among other [things](https://williamwhitaker.art), I'm a front-end developer. My focus is the space where visual design, accessible content, and code meet.  

{% endsnippet %}
</article>

<article class="flow">
  <h2>recent posts</h2>
{% snippet %}
{% if posts %}
{% for post in posts %}
<div class="flow">
    <h3>
        <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
    </h3>
    <p>{{ post.data.teaser }}</p>
</div>
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
No posts yet!
{% endif %}
{% endsnippet %}
</article>